	   <tr><td colspan=2>Somebody please answer this one.&nbsp;&nbsp;What would be the best trade for a magician to undertake.  I am level 8 and have put no points into anything except for medding (which was only 1 point).  I would like to start my trade skill.  Please advise me as to which one would be best.  Thanks!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
