	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can buy all of your level 16 and 20 pet spells in OOT. Go to the island that is right next to sister island (sister island is the first stop from FP to BB). On the island next to sister island there will be a tower, inside the tower is a lady who sells what you need. <br><br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
